The input integer `n` is greater than or equal to 1.
The length of the `words` array is equal to `n`.
The length of the `groups` array is equal to `n`.
Each string in the `words` array consists of lowercase English letters.
Each string in the `words` array has a length between 1 and 10 (inclusive).
Each element in the `groups` array is between 1 and `n` (inclusive).
The `words` array consists of distinct strings.
